			programming programming device drivers in c. When I made the career
			jump to Healthcare I ran a Claims Clearinghouse for a local private
			insurer before it was sold to a national company. I eventually went
			back the private insurer to learn enterprise server side programming
			using Java, structs, jsp and Oracle relational database. In my last
			employment I focused on developing front-end and web development
			applications.</p>
